      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly opportunity? \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is priced to move and reflects its current poor condition honestly \u2014 it's got some wear and will need repairs and attention before it's road-ready at its best. Perfect for a handy DIYer, a parts salvager, or someone looking for a affordable project to tackle! At this price point, it's a great chance to get your hands on a fixable ride without breaking the bank. Sold as-is \u2014 come see it for yourself!",
