      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project car or a budget-friendly option you can work with? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has significant wear and will need some repairs and attention before it's running at its best. That said, it represents a real opportunity for a handy buyer or someone looking to get into a vehicle at a low entry cost. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
